{"tid":1076528,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[CCTVB] 北望神州大計 TVB製作中國式綜藝節目","createTime":"2019-03-25T02:12:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-25T02:28:08.000Z","uid":56881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4b0ed27fe299e4251790b0ab1e499f170f9a529f","tid":1076528,"uid":56881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T02:12:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%8C%97%E6%9C%9B%E7%A5%9E%E5%B7%9E%E5%A4%A7%E8%A8%88-tvb%E8%A3%BD%E4%BD%9C%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%BC%8F%E7%B6%9C%E8%97%9D%E7%AF%80%E7%9B%AE-221137438.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E5%258C%2597%25E6%259C%259B%25E7%25A5%259E%25E5%25B7%259E%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E8%25A8%2588-tvb%25E8%25A3%25BD%25E4%25BD%259C%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25BC%258F%25E7%25B6%259C%25E8%2597%259D%25E7%25AF%2580%25E7%259B%25AE-221137438.html&d=Peq93FhG%2BXbpjcIFBj2O6V95pAf34VZm09NJx5vbAww%3D&h=dbfb435c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%8C%97%E6%9C%9B%E7%A5%9E%E5%B7%9E%E5%A4%A7%E8%A8%88-tvb%E8%A3%BD%E4%BD%9C%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%BC%8F%E7%B6%9C%E8%97%9D%E7%AF%80%E7%9B%AE-221137438.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/v55H1HuByOFTa.nIHlrF2g--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MzgzO2g9MjU1O2lsPXBsYW5l/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/singtao/95884.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Fv55H1HuByOFTa.nIHlrF2g--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MzgzO2g9MjU1O2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FNews%2Fsingtao%2F95884.jpg&h=4a07dead&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■TVB除製作中國式的綜藝節目，亦密謀在內地設立電視城。<br />\n<br />\n【星島日報報道】（星島日報報道）TVB入股星美如意算盤未打響，但已有其他北望神州大計。李寶安透露，將會製作中國式的綜藝節目，頭炮或是老本行選美節目，公司亦密謀在內地設立電視城。<br />\n<br />\n去年該公司收入按年增三成八至二十四點四億元，增長動力來自中國聯合製作連續劇及網上視頻，令內地收入增長兩成六。李寶安表示，近年每集合拍劇的叫價愈來愈高，預期今年保持推出三套合拍作品，未來會加強在內地發展。<br />\n<br />\n他透露，今年擬跟內地網上平合作拍攝綜藝節目，目前打算製作以往較成功的作品，例如為《香港小姐》、《國際中華小姐》等加添中國元素，憑植入式廣告帶動電商業務，甚至不排除再添選美節目，惟目前未有定案。他稱，以往香港的目標觀眾較少，日後面對內地觀眾，可大大增加預算。<br />\n<br />\n對於內地發展的長遠大計，李寶安表示，TVB計畫在大灣區興建廠房，除了作拍攝場地外，亦考慮用來招聘藝員、訓練場所等，其道具及場景或可成立有規模的公司。但他指出，早前曾在南山覓地，惟大灣區地價較貴，現時不急於作決定。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />正式真係可以改名CCTVB?<br />\n唔係已經係中國式好耐啦咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f15e6453d2a30e13a86d4bc0ce578f594fe0a8f","tid":1076528,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T02:16:53.000Z","msg":"點樣中國法<br />\n香港好聲音?"},{"pid":"72d3e2d5557bdac04fbcc5abb14d69c1e2058cad","tid":1076528,"uid":74171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T02:24:34.000Z","msg":"《香港小姐》、《國際中華小姐》等加添中國元素，<br />\n<br />\n關咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />宜家上下網轆下ig,大把人靚過佢地參選嘅人，仲睇嚟做咩<br />\n<br />\n唔係冷飯加啲美極就會吸引到人"},{"pid":"ca65d45efaba28021deeb9974e4e783e083e37db","tid":1076528,"uid":44454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T02:28:08.000Z","msg":"請唔請觀眾？喊加幾錢？"}]}